ama</span> <span begin="00:23.850" end="00:24.392">told</span> <span begin="00:24.392" end="00:24.753">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我七岁那年，妈妈告诉我</span></p><p begin="00:24.854" end="00:28.256" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:24.854" end="00:24.985">"Go</span> <span begin="00:25.345" end="00:25.627">make</span> <span begin="00:25.627" end="00:26.063">yourself</span> <span begin="00:26.063" end="00:26.379">some</span> <span begin="00:26.379" end="00:26.732">friends,</span> <span begin="00:26.732" end="00:26.850">or</span> <span begin="00:26.850" end="00:27.178">you'll</span> <span begin="00:27.178" end="00:27.393">be</span> <span begin="00:27.393" end="00:28.256">lonely"</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“去交些朋友，否则你会孤单寂寞”</span></p><p begin="00:28.357" end="00:30.701" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:28.357" end="00:28.840">Once,</span> <span begin="00:28.840" end="00:29.178">I</span> <span begin="00:29.178" end="00:29.255">was</span> <span begin="00:29.255" end="00:29.972">seven</span> <span begin="00:29.972" end="00:30.309">years</span> <span begin="00:30.309" end="00:30.701">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我七岁那年</span></p><p begin="00:36.662" end="00:40.417" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:36.662" end="00:36.841">It</span> <span begin="00:36.841" end="00:37.171">was</span> <span begin="00:37.171" end="00:37.422">a</span> <span begin="00:37.422" end="00:37.794">big-</span><span begin="00:37.794" end="00:38.202">big</span> <span begin="00:38.202" end="00:38.652">world,</span> <span begin="00:38.652" end="00:38.867">but</span> <span begin="00:38.867" end="00:39.143">we</span> <span begin="00:39.143" end="00:39.390">thought</span> <span begin="00:39.390" end="00:39.649">we</span> <span begin="00:39.649" end="00:39.909">were</span> <span begin="00:39.909" end="00:40.417">bigger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">世界很大很大，但我们自以为更强大</span></p><p begin="00:40.870" end="00:44.485" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:40.870" end="00:41.231">Pushing</span> <span begin="00:41.231" end="00:41.435">each</span> <span begin="00:41.435" end="00:41.851">other</span> <span begin="00:41.851" end="00:42.212">to</span> <span begin="00:42.212" end="00:42.418">the</span> <span begin="00:42.418" end="00:42.903">limits,</span> <span begin="00:42.903" end="00:43.198">we</span> <span begin="00:43.198" end="00:43.404">were</span> <span begin="00:43.404" end="00:43.902">learning</span> <span begin="00:43.902" end="00:44.485">quicker</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">彼此激励挑战极限，我们学得更快</span></p><p begin="00:44.916" end="00:48.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:44.916" end="00:45.148">By</span> <span begin="00:45.148" end="00:45.777">11,</span> <span begin="00:45.777" end="00:46.393">smoking</span> <span begin="00:46.393" end="00:46.694">herb</span> <span begin="00:46.694" end="00:46.850">and</span> <span begin="00:46.850" end="00:47.379">drinking</span> <span begin="00:47.379" end="00:47.936">burning</span> <span begin="00:47.936" end="00:48.440">liquor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">十一岁时，抽着大麻，喝着烈酒</span></p><p begin="00:48.894" end="00:52.334" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:48.894" end="00:49.322">Never</span> <span begin="00:49.322" end="00:49.662">rich,</span> <span begin="00:49.662" end="00:49.873">so</span> <span begin="00:49.873" end="00:50.130">we</span> <span begin="00:50.130" end="00:50.369">were</span> <span begin="00:50.369" end="00:50.612">out</span> <span begin="00:50.612" end="00:50.869">to</span> <span begin="00:50.869" end="00:51.121">make</span> <span begin="00:51.121" end="00:51.270">that</span> <span begin="00:51.270" end="00:51.906">steady</span> <span begin="00:51.906" end="00:52.334">figure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从不富裕，所以我们立志要挣大钱</span></p><p begin="00:52.393" end="00:56.780" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:52.393" end="00:52.734">Once,</span> <span begin="00:52.734" end="00:52.912">I</span> <span begin="00:52.912" end="00:53.314">was</span> <span begin="00:53.314" end="00:53.926">11</span> <span begin="00:53.926" end="00:54.369">years</span> <span begin="00:54.369" end="00:54.589">old,</span> <span begin="00:54.902" end="00:55.020">my</span> <span begin="00:55.383" end="00:55.884">daddy</span> <span begin="00:55.884" end="00:56.393">told</span> <span begin="00:56.393" end="00:56.780">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我十一岁那年，爸爸告诉我</span></p><p begin="00:56.835" end="01:00.281" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:56.835" end="00:57.095">"Go</span> <span begin="00:57.388" end="00:57.608">get</span> <span begin="00:57.608" end="00:58.220">yourself</span> <span begin="00:58.220" end="00:58.371">a</span> <span begin="00:58.371" end="00:58.729">wife,</span> <span begin="00:58.729" end="00:58.816">or</span> <span begin="00:58.816" end="00:59.191">you'll</span> <span begin="00:59.191" end="00:59.377">be</span> <span begin="00:59.377" end="01:00.281">lonely"</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“去找个妻子，否则你会孤单寂寞”</span></p><p begin="01:00.359" end="01:02.643" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:00.359" end="01:00.704">Once,</span> <span begin="01:00.704" end="01:00.919">I</span> <span begin="01:00.919" end="01:01.384">was</span> <span begin="01:01.384" end="01:01.946">11</span> <span begin="01:01.946" end="01:02.372">years</span> <span begin="01:02.372" end="01:02.643">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我十一岁那年</span></p><p begin="01:08.696" end="01:12.447" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:08.696" end="01:08.874">I</span> <span begin="01:08.874" end="01:09.443">always</span> <span begin="01:09.443" end="01:09.830">had</span> <span begin="01:09.830" end="01:10.193">that</span> <span begin="01:10.193" end="01:10.496">dream</span> <span begin="01:10.496" end="01:11.179">like</span> <span begin="01:11.179" end="01:11.354">my</span> <span begin="01:11.354" end="01:11.679">daddy</span> <span begin="01:11.679" end="01:12.216">before</span> <span begin="01:12.216" end="01:12.447">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我总怀揣着和父亲一样的梦想</span></p><p begin="01:12.626" end="01:16.487" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:12.626" end="01:13.161">So</span> <span begin="01:13.161" end="01:13.257">I</span> <span begin="01:13.257" end="01:13.868">started</span> <span begin="01:13.868" end="01:14.281">writing</span> <span begin="01:14.281" end="01:14.716">songs,</span> <span begin="01:14.716" end="01:14.791">I</span> <span begin="01:14.791" end="01:15.345">started</span> <span begin="01:15.345" end="01:15.783">writing</span> <span begin="01:15.783" end="01:16.487">stories</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">于是我开始了写歌，开始了写故事</span></p><p begin="01:16.624" end="01:20.442" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:16.624" end="01:17.185">Something</span> <span begin="01:17.185" end="01:17.703">about</span> <span begin="01:17.703" end="01:17.923">the</span> <span begin="01:17.923" end="01:18.653">glory</span> <span begin="01:18.653" end="01:18.875">just</span> <span begin="01:18.875" end="01:19.333">always</span> <span begin="01:19.333" end="01:19.681">seemed</span> <span begin="01:19.681" end="01:19.883">to</span> <span begin="01:19.883" end="01:20.204">bore</span> <span begin="01:20.204" end="01:20.442">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那些所谓的荣耀总让我觉得无趣</span></p><p begin="01:20.666" end="01:24.345" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:20.666" end="01:20.932">'Cause</span> <span begin="01:20.932" end="01:21.357">only</span> <span begin="01:21.357" end="01:21.709">those</span> <span begin="01:21.709" end="01:21.851">I</span> <span begin="01:21.851" end="01:22.324">really</span> <span begin="01:22.324" end="01:22.680">love</span> <span begin="01:22.680" end="01:22.917">will</span> <span begin="01:22.917" end="01:23.364">ever</span> <span begin="01:23.364" end="01:23.883">really</span> <span begin="01:23.883" end="01:24.184">know</span> <span begin="01:24.184" end="01:24.345">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为只有我真正爱的人才能真正了解我</span></p><p begin="01:24.382" end="01:28.591" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:24.382" end="01:24.873">Once,</span> <span begin="01:24.873" end="01:25.172">I</span> <span begin="01:25.172" end="01:25.358">was</span> <span begin="01:25.358" end="01:25.927">20</span> <span begin="01:25.927" end="01:26.360">years</span> <span begin="01:26.360" end="01:26.862">old,</span> <span begin="01:26.862" end="01:27.266">my</span> <span begin="01:27.266" end="01:27.846">story</span> <span begin="01:27.846" end="01:28.329">got</span> <span begin="01:28.329" end="01:28.591">told</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年，我的故事被传唱</span></p><p begin="01:29.169" end="01:32.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:29.169" end="01:29.682">Before</span> <span begin="01:29.682" end="01:29.887">the</span> <span begin="01:29.887" end="01:30.326">morning</span> <span begin="01:30.326" end="01:30.669">sun,</span> <span begin="01:30.669" end="01:30.868">when</span> <span begin="01:30.868" end="01:31.263">life</span> <span begin="01:31.263" end="01:31.455">was</span> <span begin="01:31.455" end="01:32.280">lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在清晨的太阳升起之前，生活曾那么孤单</span></p><p begin="01:32.363" end="01:37.146" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:32.363" end="01:32.903">Once,</span> <span begin="01:32.903" end="01:33.197">I</span> <span begin="01:33.197" end="01:33.366">was</span> <span begin="01:33.366" end="01:33.884">20</span> <span begin="01:33.884" end="01:34.332">years</span> <span begin="01:34.332" end="01:35.280">old</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:35.744" end="01:37.146"><span begin="01:35.744" end="01:36.211">(Lukas</span> <span begin="01:36.211" end="01:37.146">Graham!)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">卢卡斯·格雷厄姆！</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年</span></p><p begin="01:40.715" end="01:44.530" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:40.715" end="01:40.876">I</span> <span begin="01:40.876" end="01:41.302">only</span> <span begin="01:41.302" end="01:41.820">see</span> <span begin="01:41.820" end="01:42.163">my</span> <span begin="01:42.163" end="01:42.620">goals,</span> <span begin="01:42.620" end="01:42.870">I</span> <span begin="01:42.870" end="01:43.143">don't</span> <span begin="01:43.194" end="01:43.711">believe</span> <span begin="01:43.711" end="01:43.958">in</span> <span begin="01:43.958" end="01:44.530">failure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只看到我的目标，我不相信失败</span></p><p begin="01:44.691" end="01:48.338" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:44.691" end="01:45.207">'Cause</span> <span begin="01:45.207" end="01:45.368">I</span> <span begin="01:45.368" end="01:45.698">know</span> <span begin="01:45.698" end="01:45.775">the</span> <span begin="01:45.775" end="01:46.363">smallest</span> <span begin="01:46.363" end="01:46.928">voices,</span> <span begin="01:46.928" end="01:47.184">they</span> <span begin="01:47.184" end="01:47.363">can</span> <span begin="01:47.363" end="01:47.703">make</span> <span begin="01:47.703" end="01:47.873">it</span> <span begin="01:47.873" end="01:48.338">major</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我知道最微小的声音也能成就大事</span></p><p begin="01:48.696" end="01:52.486" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:48.696" end="01:48.873">I</span> <span begin="01:48.873" end="01:49.107">got</span> <span begin="01:49.107" end="01:49.348">my</span> <span begin="01:49.348" end="01:49.873">boys</span> <span begin="01:49.873" end="01:50.136">with</span> <span begin="01:50.136" end="01:50.349">me,</span> <span begin="01:50.689" end="01:50.859">at</span> <span begin="01:50.859" end="01:51.350">least</span> <span begin="01:51.350" end="01:51.709">those</span> <span begin="01:51.709" end="01:51.873">in</span> <span begin="01:51.873" end="01:52.486">favor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我有我的兄弟们陪着我，至少是那些支持我的</span></p><p begin="01:52.701" end="01:56.357" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:52.701" end="01:52.879">And</span> <span begin="01:52.879" end="01:53.044">if</span> <span begin="01:53.044" end="01:53.159">we</span> <span begin="01:53.159" end="01:53.304">don't</span> <span begin="01:53.304" end="01:53.713">meet</span> <span begin="01:53.713" end="01:54.161">before</span> <span begin="01:54.161" end="01:54.354">I</span> <span begin="01:54.354" end="01:54.680">leave,</span> <span begin="01:54.680" end="01:54.869">I</span> <span begin="01:54.869" end="01:55.149">hope</span> <span begin="01:55.149" end="01:55.294">I'll</span> <span begin="01:55.294" end="01:55.665">see</span> <span begin="01:55.665" end="01:55.871">you</span> <span begin="01:55.871" end="01:56.357">later</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果我离开前没能见到你，希望后会有期</span></p><p begin="01:56.357" end="02:00.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:56.357" end="01:56.864">Once,</span> <span begin="01:56.864" end="01:57.178">I</span> <span begin="01:57.178" end="01:57.360">was</span> <span begin="01:57.360" end="01:57.882">20</span> <span begin="01:57.882" end="01:58.300">years</span> <span begin="01:58.300" end="01:58.871">old,</span> <span begin="01:58.871" end="01:59.154">my</span> <span begin="01:59.154" end="01:59.887">story</span> <span begin="01:59.887" end="02:00.330">got</span> <span begin="02:00.330" end="02:00.850">told</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年，我的故事被传唱</span></p><p begin="02:00.850" end="02:04.054" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:00.850" end="02:01.009">I</span> <span begin="02:01.009" end="02:01.215">was</span> <span begin="02:01.215" end="02:01.735">writing</span> <span begin="02:01.735" end="02:01.921">'bout</span> <span begin="02:01.921" end="02:02.551">everything,</span> <span begin="02:02.551" end="02:02.812">I</span> <span begin="02:02.812" end="02:03.186">saw</span> <span begin="02:03.186" end="02:03.878">before</span> <span begin="02:03.878" end="02:04.054">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我写下眼前的一切</span></p><p begin="02:04.381" end="02:06.648" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:04.381" end="02:04.870">Once,</span> <span begin="02:04.870" end="02:05.095">I</span> <span begin="02:05.095" end="02:05.384">was</span> <span begin="02:05.384" end="02:05.867">20</span> <span begin="02:05.867" end="02:06.315">years</span> <span begin="02:06.315" end="02:06.648">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年</span></p><p begin="02:12.272" end="02:16.667" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:12.272" end="02:12.869">Soon,</span> <span begin="02:12.869" end="02:13.176">we'll</span> <span begin="02:13.176" end="02:13.357">be</span> <span begin="02:13.357" end="02:13.902">30</span> <span begin="02:13.902" end="02:14.344">years</span> <span begin="02:14.344" end="02:14.846">old,</span> <span begin="02:14.846" end="02:15.257">our</span> <span begin="02:15.257" end="02:15.733">songs</span> <span begin="02:15.733" end="02:15.897">have</span> <span begin="02:15.897" end="02:16.236">been</span> <span begin="02:16.236" end="02:16.667">sold</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我们将到三十岁，我们的歌已被传唱</span></p><p begin="02:16.871" end="02:20.065" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:16.871" end="02:17.333">We've</span> <span begin="02:17.333" end="02:17.783">traveled</span> <span begin="02:17.783" end="02:18.222">around</span> <span begin="02:18.222" end="02:18.418">the</span> <span begin="02:18.418" end="02:18.741">world,</span> <span begin="02:18.741" end="02:18.917">and</span> <span begin="02:18.917" end="02:19.079">we're</span> <span begin="02:19.079" end="02:19.500">still</span> <span begin="02:19.500" end="02:20.065">roaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们环游世界，仍在四处漂泊</span></p><p begin="02:20.284" end="02:22.691" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:20.284" end="02:20.866">Soon,</span> <span begin="02:20.866" end="02:21.172">we'll</span> <span begin="02:21.172" end="02:21.285">be</span> <span begin="02:21.285" end="02:21.937">30</span> <span begin="02:21.937" end="02:22.342">years</span> <span begin="02:22.342" end="02:22.691">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我们将到三十岁</span></p><p begin="02:28.652" end="02:32.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:28.652" end="02:28.765">I'm</span> <span begin="02:28.765" end="02:29.376">still</span> <span begin="02:29.376" end="02:29.763">learning</span> <span begin="02:29.763" end="02:30.168">about</span> <span begin="02:30.168" end="02:30.694">life,</span> <span begin="02:30.694" end="02:30.877">my</span> <span begin="02:30.877" end="02:31.133">woman</span> <span begin="02:31.133" end="02:31.336">brought</span> <span begin="02:31.336" end="02:31.866">children</span> <span begin="02:31.866" end="02:32.223">for</span> <span begin="02:32.223" end="02:32.570">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我仍在学习人生，我的女人为我生了孩子</span></p><p begin="02:32.610" end="02:36.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:32.610" end="02:32.911">So</span> <span begin="02:32.911" end="02:33.177">I</span> <span begin="02:33.177" end="02:33.310">can</span> <span begin="02:33.310" end="02:33.681">sing</span> <span begin="02:33.681" end="02:33.889">them</span> <span begin="02:33.889" end="02:34.105">all</span> <span begin="02:34.105" end="02:34.263">my</span> <span begin="02:34.263" end="02:34.702">songs,</span> <span begin="02:34.702" end="02:34.870">and</span> <span begin="02:34.870" end="02:35.079">I</span> <span begin="02:35.079" end="02:35.277">can</span> <span begin="02:35.277" end="02:35.576">tell</span> <span begin="02:35.576" end="02:35.715">them</span> <span begin="02:35.715" end="02:36.420">stories</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这样我就可以给他们唱我所有的歌，给他们讲我的故事</span></p><p begin="02:36.588" end="02:40.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:36.588" end="02:36.875">Most</span> <span begin="02:36.875" end="02:37.102">of</span> <span begin="02:37.102" end="02:37.325">my</span> <span begin="02:37.325" end="02:37.680">boys</span> <span begin="02:37.680" end="02:37.857">are</span> <span begin="02:37.857" end="02:38.160">with</span> <span begin="02:38.160" end="02:38.269">me,</span> <span begin="02:38.269" end="02:38.605">some</span> <span begin="02:38.605" end="02:38.739">are</span> <span begin="02:38.739" end="02:39.145">still</span> <span begin="02:39.145" end="02:39.305">out</span> <span begin="02:39.305" end="02:39.894">seeking</span> <span begin="02:39.894" end="02:40.420">glory</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的大多数兄弟还在我身边，有些仍在追寻荣耀</span></p><p begin="02:40.647" end="02:44.321" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:40.647" end="02:40.752">And</span> <span begin="02:40.752" end="02:41.131">some</span> <span begin="02:41.131" end="02:41.306">I</span> <span begin="02:41.306" end="02:41.651">had</span> <span begin="02:41.651" end="02:41.905">to</span> <span begin="02:41.905" end="02:42.161">leave</span> <span begin="02:42.161" end="02:42.683">behind,</span> <span begin="02:42.683" end="02:42.871">my</span> <span begin="02:42.871" end="02:43.377">brother,</span> <span begin="02:43.377" end="02:43.538">I'm</span> <span begin="02:43.538" end="02:43.816">still</span> <span begin="02:43.816" end="02:44.321">sorry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有些我不得不让他们离开，我的兄弟，我至今仍感抱歉</span></p><p begin="02:44.321" end="02:48.561" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:44.321" end="02:44.880">Soon,</spa