150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:56.700" end="02:56.874">I</span> <span begin="02:56.874" end="02:57.158">hope</span> <span begin="02:57.158" end="02:57.305">my</span> <span begin="02:57.305" end="02:57.834">children</span> <span begin="02:57.834" end="02:58.172">come</span> <span begin="02:58.172" end="02:58.357">and</span> <span begin="02:58.357" end="02:58.857">visit,</span> <span begin="02:58.857" end="02:59.176">once</span> <span begin="02:59.176" end="02:59.288">or</span> <span begin="02:59.288" end="02:59.715">twice</span> <span begin="02:59.715" end="02:59.858">a</span> <span begin="02:59.858" end="03:00.150">month</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我希望我的孩子们能来看望我，一月一次或两次</span></p><p begin="03:00.214" end="03:04.670" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="03:00.214" end="03:00.780">Soon,</span> <span begin="03:00.780" end="03:01.125">I'll</span> <span begin="03:01.125" end="03:01.308">be</span> <span begin="03:01.308" end="03:01.842">60</span> <span begin="03:01.842" end="03:02.360">years</span> <span begin="03:02.360" end="03:02.844">old,</span> <span begin="03:02.844" end="03:02.944">will</span> <span begin="03:02.944" end="03:03.346">I</span> <span begin="03:03.346" end="03:03.678">think</span> <span begin="03:03.678" end="03:03.867">the</span> <span begin="03:03.867" end="03:04.162">world</span> <span begin="03:04.162" end="03:04.323">is</span> <span begin="03:04.323" end="03:04.670">cold?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我将到六十岁，我会觉得这世界冷漠吗？</span></p><p begin="03:04.670" end="03:08.322" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:04.670" end="03:04.864">Or</span> <span begin="03:04.864" end="03:04.984">will</span> <span begin="03:04.984" end="03:05.320">I</span> <span begin="03:05.320" end="03:05.667">have</span> <span begin="03:05.667" end="03:05.824">a</span> <span begin="03:05.824" end="03:06.122">lot</span> <span begin="03:06.122" end="03:06.276">of</span> <span begin="03:06.276" end="03:06.863">children</span> <span begin="03:06.863" end="03:07.097">who</span> <span begin="03:07.097" end="03:07.355">can</span> <span begin="03:07.355" end="03:07.838">warm</span> <span begin="03:07.838" end="03:08.322">me?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还是会有一大群孩子温暖我的心？</span></p><p begin="03:08.322" end="03:10.857" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:08.322" end="03:08.856">Soon,</span> <span begin="03:08.856" end="03:09.150">I'll</span> <span begin="03:09.150" end="03:09.291">be</span> <span begin="03:09.291" end="03:09.972">60</span> <span begin="03:09.972" end="03:10.347">years</span> <span begin="03:10.347" end="03:10.857">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我将到六十岁</span></p><p begin="03:16.244" end="03:20.654" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:16.244" end="03:16.881">Soon,</span> <span begin="03:16.881" end="03:17.197">I'll</span> <span begin="03:17.197" end="03:17.300">be</span> <span begin="03:17.300" end="03:17.879">60</span> <span begin="03:17.879" end="03:18.298">years</span> <span begin="03:18.298" end="03:18.850">old,</span> <span begin="03:18.850" end="03:18.981">will</span> <span begin="03:18.981" end="03:19.366">I</span> <span begin="03:19.366" end="03:19.685">think</span> <span begin="03:19.685" end="03:19.887">the</span> <span begin="03:19.887" end="03:20.136">world</span> <span begin="03:20.136" end="03:20.323">is</span> <span begin="03:20.323" end="03:20.654">cold?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我将到六十岁，我会觉得这世界冷漠吗？</span></p><p begin="03:20.694" end="03:24.143" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:20.694" end="03:20.840">Or</span> <span begin="03:20.840" end="03:20.974">will</span> <span begin="03:20.974" end="03:21.335">I</span> <span begin="03:21.335" end="03:21.682">have</span> <span begin="03:21.682" end="03:21.860">a</span> <span begin="03:21.860" end="03:22.146">lot</span> <span begin="03:22.146" end="03:22.362">of</span> <s